column5: Heading to Qunite Saturday anyone been this week and how was your luck?    Ken
Was there for the opener, caught all our fish at night.  Good luck.
Saturday of  opener was a  good day sunday skunked went out yesterday as well only one and that was it.

Went out after I closed the store tonight and got a couple of eaters.  The best time is in the evening and at night.  Will be heading out again tomorrow night as well in themouth of the rivers.  That seems to be productive and getting you the eating size a couple of pounds each.  Best regards, Sam
